body:
I want to find out what causes the error `vvp.tgt error: Thread words exhausted.` to be thrown. For example the module below causes that error.
```
module dut #(parameter i_width=64, o_width=128)(input logic[i_width-1:0] a, b, output logic [o_width-1:0] out );
integer i;
always @(a or b)
begin
out=1'b0;
for(i=0;i<i_width;i=i+1)begin
if(a[i]==1'b1)
begin
out=~(b>>(a+(out>>(out>>(i>>(~(a<<(~(~(~(i<<(a<<(a>>(~(i<<(a+(out<<(out>>(~(a+(b<<(~(~(~(~(~(~(b<<(~(out))))))))))))))))))))))))))))));
end
end
end
endmodule
```

